動及周末寶珠關卡<br />\n【7】逢<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">星期五至日</span></strong>都會開週末寶珠關,新手建議先刷Rank上100UP加多D體,基本唔洗爆石無限升的<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">オトモン属性耐性表</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mhr/zokusei.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmhr%2Fzokusei.jpg&h=3c1cd68b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">升LV70必要寶玉/禮物數</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xgoFCix.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxgoFCix.jpg&h=61cbe401&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【常見問題】</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><strong>◆護符有咩用,買左加護LV都唔升◆</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M4nP8BF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM4nP8BF.jpg&h=b952f4de&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n各都市加護LV需要一定經驗值先會升,<br />\n而經驗值就係你BOX入面所有相對都市人既合計LV+合計護符數量,<br />\n人每升1LV=1EXP<br />\n護符1個=1EXP<br />\n所以護符買左就OK,咩都唔洗做"},{"pid":"48507a9d12bf55b971b30b08f8b0abab69a778e4","tid":2083677,"uid":20601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:17:31.000Z","msg":"人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a5b665a508846325bf84f7f72df722eea95441","tid":2083677,"uid":114487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:17:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9HE0Php.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9HE0Php.jpg&h=c5e5f272&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c77cbd487ef9f026eb91a17ce0bab5af2c9cf613","tid":2083677,"uid":18071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:57:17.000Z","m